WEBVTT

00:00:00.910 --> 00:00:03.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Huh? You're going
to Hokkaido tonight?</b></Default>

00:00:03.750 --> 00:00:06.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai came over to cook dinner
for us. Are you sure?</b></Default>

00:00:07.250 --> 00:00:08.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] <i>Sakuta?</i></b></Default>

00:00:08.619 --> 00:00:10.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'm sorry, Mai.</b></Default>

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:11.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to head over
to Hokkaido</b></Default>

00:00:11.449 --> 00:00:12.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to go see Fukuyama.</b></Default>

00:00:12.869 --> 00:00:14.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI]<i> Right now?</i></b></Default>

00:00:14.199 --> 00:00:15.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] It turns out
the only one</b></Default>

00:00:15.289 --> 00:00:18.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who can cure Nene Imamizawa's
Puberty Syndrome is him.</b></Default>

00:00:18.829 --> 00:00:20.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I promise
that I'll make it back</b></Default>

00:00:20.329 --> 00:00:21.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for the event tomorrow.</b></Default>

00:00:21.829 --> 00:00:23.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, please take care
of Kaede for me.</b></Default>

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:25.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] <i>Well, alright.</i></b></Default>

00:00:25.660 --> 00:00:27.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Then, I'll stay over</i>
<i>at your place tonight.</i></b></Default>

00:00:27.620 --> 00:00:29.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That actually makes me
want to rush home right now.</b></Default>

00:00:29.910 --> 00:00:32.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you come home</b></Default>

00:00:32.119 --> 00:00:33.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just be careful, okay?</b></Default>

00:00:33.789 --> 00:00:35.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] <i>Oh, yeah. Hey, Mai.</i></b></Default>

00:00:35.369 --> 00:00:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:00:36.579 --> 00:00:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] <i>I love you.</i></b></Default>

00:00:37.829 --> 00:00:39.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Hamburg steaks
will char soon</b></Default>

00:00:39.619 --> 00:00:41.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so call me when you get there.</b></Default>

00:00:42.250 --> 00:00:44.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Ready, Azusagawa?
-[SAKUTA] Hmm.</b></Default>

00:00:44.659 --> 00:00:46.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>HANEDA AIRPORT</b></Default>

00:00:47.250 --> 00:00:48.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>TOUKO KIRISHIMA</b></Default>

00:00:49.039 --> 00:00:51.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ soft music playing]</b></Default>

00:00:59.289 --> 00:01:00.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks
for lending me your phone.</b></Default>

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No problem.</b></Default>

00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:05.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyways, you really don't mind
tagging along with me?</b></Default>

00:01:06.040 --> 00:01:07.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] If this
has something to do</b></Default>

00:01:07.290 --> 00:01:09.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the message
from the other world</b></Default>

00:01:09.370 --> 00:01:11.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to see it through, too.</b></Default>

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:15.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct announcements]</b></Default>

00:01:19.290 --> 00:01:20.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind blowing]</b></Default>

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] <i>Do you recognize</i>
<i>this trophy?</i></b></Default>

00:01:29.079 --> 00:01:30.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, not at all.</b></Default>

00:01:30.370 --> 00:01:31.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why I threw it away.</b></Default>

00:01:31.790 --> 00:01:33.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So you
really don't understand</b></Default>

00:01:33.290 --> 00:01:35.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're actually Nene Iwamizawa?</b></Default>

00:01:35.159 --> 00:01:37.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no idea
who Nene Iwamizawa is.</b></Default>

00:01:37.620 --> 00:01:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you stop asking?</b></Default>

00:01:38.950 --> 00:01:40.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MISS CUY CONTEST
64TH GRAND PRIZE</b></Default>

00:01:40.409 --> 00:01:41.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] I've had enough
for today.</b></Default>

00:01:42.700 --> 00:01:45.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go home
and throw that away, okay?</b></Default>

00:01:51.790 --> 00:01:53.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I get it now.</b></Default>

00:01:53.079 --> 00:01:55.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her life as Nene Iwamizawa
is what she threw out.</b></Default>

00:01:57.620 --> 00:01:59.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:03:05.500 --> 00:03:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:30.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NO DREAMS OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:03:36.949 --> 00:03:37.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh.</b></Default>

00:03:37.949 --> 00:03:40.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't actually think
you'd come all this way.</b></Default>

00:03:40.409 --> 00:03:41.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I said I would, didn't I?</b></Default>

00:03:41.909 --> 00:03:43.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry it's so abrupt.</b></Default>

00:03:43.449 --> 00:03:45.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] No, no</b></Default>

00:03:46.199 --> 00:03:48.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One sec.
I'm gonna go call my family.</b></Default>

00:03:50.830 --> 00:03:52.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] So, what's your plan?
You know</b></Default>

00:03:52.830 --> 00:03:54.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where you're staying the night
and stuff?</b></Default>

00:03:54.909 --> 00:03:56.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's that you got
in your pocket?</b></Default>

00:03:59.699 --> 00:04:00.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A trophy.</b></Default>

00:04:01.289 --> 00:04:02.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you recognize it?</b></Default>

00:04:02.699 --> 00:04:04.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ suspenseful music playing]</b></Default>

00:04:17.199 --> 00:04:18.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

00:04:23.079 --> 00:04:24.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps softly]</b></Default>

00:04:25.660 --> 00:04:26.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:04:27.290 --> 00:04:29.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fukuyama, calm down
and remember.</b></Default>

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:31.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] That's not it</b></Default>

00:04:31.910 --> 00:04:32.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:04:33.540 --> 00:04:34.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] Cause...</b></Default>

00:04:35.160 --> 00:04:36.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean...</b></Default>

00:04:36.870 --> 00:04:37.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she was...</b></Default>

00:04:38.660 --> 00:04:40.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she was ecstatic about this.</b></Default>

00:04:41.160 --> 00:04:43.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was the grand prize winner</b></Default>

00:04:43.199 --> 00:04:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she had the biggest smile.</b></Default>

00:04:45.329 --> 00:04:46.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nene was...</b></Default>

00:04:46.699 --> 00:04:47.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathes shakily]</b></Default>

00:04:47.910 --> 00:04:49.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Takumi whimpers] Why?</b></Default>

00:04:49.199 --> 00:04:51.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why had I forgotten
about her until now?</b></Default>

00:04:52.410 --> 00:04:53.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sobs]</b></Default>

00:04:54.910 --> 00:04:56.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ sad music playing]</b></Default>

00:05:02.410 --> 00:05:04.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'd say
this makes coming all the way</b></Default>

00:05:04.370 --> 00:05:05.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to Hokkaido worth it.</b></Default>

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:10.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] What do you think
I should do?</b></Default>

00:05:11.699 --> 00:05:13.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, the only thing
that can save her now</b></Default>

00:05:13.699 --> 00:05:15.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is the power
of your love, Fukuyama.</b></Default>

00:05:15.829 --> 00:05:18.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had forgotten her
for close to a year already.</b></Default>

00:05:18.250 --> 00:05:20.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Am I even qualified
to talk about loving her?</b></Default>

00:05:20.579 --> 00:05:23.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you aren't qualified</b></Default>

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-So, hold yourself together.
-[chuckles]</b></Default>

00:05:26.290 --> 00:05:27.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Haven't been scolded in a while.</b></Default>

00:05:28.040 --> 00:05:29.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hurry up
and get your girlfriend back</b></Default>

00:05:30.040 --> 00:05:31.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she can scold you to death.</b></Default>

00:05:31.790 --> 00:05:34.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nene sure is scary
when she's angry, though.</b></Default>

00:05:34.750 --> 00:05:36.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I finally asked her out</b></Default>

00:05:36.290 --> 00:05:37.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she scolded me
with a "you're so late"</b></Default>

00:05:37.949 --> 00:05:39.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before saying yes.</b></Default>

00:05:39.079 --> 00:05:40.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And when you
didn't get into uni?</b></Default>

00:05:40.829 --> 00:05:42.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The first time it happened</b></Default>

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:44.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she cried
and asked me "why not?"</b></Default>

00:05:44.120 --> 00:05:45.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the second time she was kind</b></Default>

00:05:45.910 --> 00:05:47.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and told me
not to push myself too hard.</b></Default>

00:05:48.949 --> 00:05:51.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In her hometown</b></Default>

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:53.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sometimes</b></Default>

00:05:53.949 --> 00:05:55.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to do a bit of modeling work.</b></Default>

00:05:56.120 --> 00:05:57.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But then</b></Default>

00:05:57.250 --> 00:05:58.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when she moved to Tokyo</b></Default>

00:05:58.829 --> 00:06:00.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>work didn't pick up
the way she had hoped.</b></Default>

00:06:01.329 --> 00:06:02.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She won first place</b></Default>

00:06:02.410 --> 00:06:04.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the Miss Campus Contest</b></Default>

00:06:04.370 --> 00:06:06.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Actually</b></Default>

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:07.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she wanted to become
an announcer</b></Default>

00:06:07.449 --> 00:06:09.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for a TV station in Tokyo.</b></Default>

00:06:09.290 --> 00:06:11.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Miss Campus Contest
was step one</b></Default>

00:06:11.699 --> 00:06:14.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and that's why
she was really happy about it.</b></Default>

00:06:14.120 --> 00:06:16.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her singing talent was the talk
of the town.</b></Default>

00:06:16.579 --> 00:06:18.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They said she
sounded like Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:06:18.790 --> 00:06:20.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That she
was just like the real thing.</b></Default>

00:06:20.949 --> 00:06:22.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But she took it literally.</b></Default>

00:06:22.500 --> 00:06:24.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now she's saying
she is Touko Kirishima</b></Default>

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:27.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and completely believes that
to be true.</b></Default>

00:06:27.949 --> 00:06:29.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] I guess
there was just a lot</b></Default>

00:06:29.370 --> 00:06:30.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of disconnect.</b></Default>

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:33.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's really
only a slight disconnect</b></Default>

00:06:33.410 --> 00:06:34.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with you, as well.</b></Default>

00:06:35.079 --> 00:06:36.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you guys
can still figure it out.</b></Default>

00:06:37.750 --> 00:06:39.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps so.</b></Default>

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:40.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, you can.</b></Default>

00:06:42.449 --> 00:06:44.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hey, Azusagawa.
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:06:46.079 --> 00:06:48.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know, I really do love Nene.</b></Default>

00:06:50.699 --> 00:06:53.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like, I really love her.</b></Default>

00:06:53.620 --> 00:06:55.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then make sure to say that
to her face tomorrow.</b></Default>

00:06:56.620 --> 00:06:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[machine buzzing]</b></Default>

00:06:58.870 --> 00:07:00.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>TEA / WATER
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRINK</b></Default>

00:07:00.500 --> 00:07:01.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:07:05.620 --> 00:07:06.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Thanks a lot
for reserving</b></Default>

00:07:06.790 --> 00:07:08.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>our tickets back home.</b></Default>

00:07:08.250 --> 00:07:10.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It lands in Haneda at 9:10</b></Default>

00:07:10.410 --> 00:07:13.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so we'll just barely make it
back to the event at one.</b></Default>

00:07:13.199 --> 00:07:15.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really, Akagi.
You being here is a lifesaver.</b></Default>

00:07:16.290 --> 00:07:17.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You even researched
and found this place</b></Default>

00:07:17.949 --> 00:07:18.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for us tonight.</b></Default>

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:21.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, it's because I
needed a place to stay, too.</b></Default>

00:07:23.040 --> 00:07:24.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Question, Akagi.</b></Default>

00:07:24.410 --> 00:07:25.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's up?</b></Default>

00:07:25.540 --> 00:07:26.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] What'd you think
after hearing</b></Default>

00:07:26.790 --> 00:07:28.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about Fukuyama's girlfriend?</b></Default>

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:31.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it's something
that happens pretty often.</b></Default>

00:07:31.579 --> 00:07:33.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Didn't the same thing
happen to you</b></Default>

00:07:33.620 --> 00:07:35.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you couldn't find yourself?</b></Default>

00:07:35.410 --> 00:07:37.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or when you lost sight
of yourself?</b></Default>

00:07:37.540 --> 00:07:38.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, that's true.</b></Default>

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:42.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I still remember it so clearly.</b></Default>

00:07:42.540 --> 00:07:44.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Back when I was in kindergarten</b></Default>

00:07:44.290 --> 00:07:45.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my friend's mom told me</b></Default>

00:07:45.910 --> 00:07:48.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Little Ikumi</b></Default>

00:07:48.949 --> 00:07:50.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hearing that made me happy.</b></Default>

00:07:50.750 --> 00:07:52.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I wanted more compliments.</b></Default>

00:07:52.660 --> 00:07:54.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I kept being good.</b></Default>

00:07:54.540 --> 00:07:56.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks to that. By the time
I got to middle school</b></Default>

00:07:56.829 --> 00:07:59.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everyone laughed at me
for being way too serious.</b></Default>

00:07:59.949 --> 00:08:01.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That makes sense.</b></Default>

00:08:01.290 --> 00:08:03.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, you don't really
remember that, do you?</b></Default>

00:08:03.660 --> 00:08:05.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nah, I remember.</b></Default>

00:08:05.449 --> 00:08:08.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You erased the blackboard
cleaner than anyone else, right?</b></Default>

00:08:09.329 --> 00:08:11.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought that being that way
was being myself.</b></Default>

00:08:13.040 --> 00:08:16.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So back then, I never felt
it was hard to live in my shoes.</b></Default>

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:18.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A world-class student.</b></Default>

00:08:18.410 --> 00:08:20.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it all began
with one simple good girl.</b></Default>

00:08:21.660 --> 00:08:23.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe for Nene Iwamizawa</b></Default>

00:08:23.660 --> 00:08:26.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>being told "You sound
like Touko Kirishima"</b></Default>

00:08:26.120 --> 00:08:27.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was the catalyst she needed</b></Default>

00:08:27.449 --> 00:08:29.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to forge the identity
she always wanted.</b></Default>

00:08:30.620 --> 00:08:32.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you ever had an experience
like that?</b></Default>

00:08:33.659 --> 00:08:35.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once before.</b></Default>

00:08:35.159 --> 00:08:37.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone told me</b></Default>

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:38.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I thought I really could.</b></Default>

00:08:39.250 --> 00:08:41.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You still believe that
to this day.</b></Default>

00:08:41.750 --> 00:08:43.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thinking about it now</b></Default>

00:08:43.159 --> 00:08:45.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it really
is just like what you said.</b></Default>

00:08:45.659 --> 00:08:46.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:08:47.250 --> 00:08:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a common tale
that happens everywhere.</b></Default>

00:08:52.870 --> 00:08:55.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FEBRUARY 4TH</b></Default>

00:08:58.120 --> 00:09:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ tense music playing]</b></Default>

00:09:00.330 --> 00:09:01.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:09:02.250 --> 00:09:03.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[brakes screech]</b></Default>

00:09:09.370 --> 00:09:11.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell ringing]</b></Default>

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:13.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa, move over.</b></Default>

00:09:13.120 --> 00:09:14.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You had a spare key on you?</b></Default>

00:09:14.830 --> 00:09:16.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Obviously, I am her boyfriend.</b></Default>

00:09:17.700 --> 00:09:20.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Nene! It's me!
I can come in, right?</b></Default>

00:09:23.950 --> 00:09:24.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:09:25.870 --> 00:09:26.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[hesitates]</b></Default>

00:09:27.620 --> 00:09:29.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She dresses up
as a miniskirt Santa, too.</b></Default>

00:09:29.870 --> 00:09:31.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So don't get freaked out
when you see her.</b></Default>

00:09:31.950 --> 00:09:33.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm looking forward
to seeing that.</b></Default>

00:09:33.909 --> 00:09:35.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the spirit!</b></Default>

00:09:35.539 --> 00:09:37.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I last came in here</b></Default>

00:09:37.080 --> 00:09:39.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this room didn't look anything
like this, you know?</b></Default>

00:09:40.500 --> 00:09:42.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And she had her trophy placed
right here on her desk.</b></Default>

00:09:43.080 --> 00:09:44.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

00:09:44.700 --> 00:09:46.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FEBRUARY 4TH: POLICE CHIEF
FOR A DAY MAI SAKURAJIMA</b></Default>

00:09:46.409 --> 00:09:47.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>TIME: 13:00 TO 14:00 TRAFFIC
ACCIDENT PREVENTION AWARENESS</b></Default>

00:09:47.409 --> 00:09:48.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] This can't be real.</b></Default>

00:09:49.250 --> 00:09:51.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is Nene seriously thinking
about doing something</b></Default>

00:09:51.659 --> 00:09:53.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to Sakurajima today?</b></Default>

00:09:54.580 --> 00:09:57.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] Does Iwamizawa
normally travel by train?</b></Default>

00:09:57.159 --> 00:09:58.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When we went to Motomachi
the other day</b></Default>

00:09:58.950 --> 00:09:59.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she rented a car.</b></Default>

00:09:59.950 --> 00:10:01.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a rental place
next to the station.</b></Default>

00:10:01.870 --> 00:10:03.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a safe bet she went there!</b></Default>

00:10:04.000 --> 00:10:06.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:10:08.830 --> 00:10:11.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi, I'll leave this to you
and pay you back.</b></Default>

00:10:11.250 --> 00:10:12.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] Got it.</b></Default>

00:10:14.039 --> 00:10:15.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:24.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Hey! Wait up, Nene!</b></Default>

00:10:27.330 --> 00:10:28.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nene!</b></Default>

00:10:29.200 --> 00:10:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fukuyama, watch out!</b></Default>

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:32.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs, gasps]</b></Default>

00:10:32.909 --> 00:10:34.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nene, please listen to me!</b></Default>

00:10:43.120 --> 00:10:44.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, just hear me out.</b></Default>

00:10:44.750 --> 00:10:46.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] This is surprising.</b></Default>

00:10:46.159 --> 00:10:48.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you're another person
who can see me, huh?</b></Default>

00:10:48.539 --> 00:10:51.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Another person? It's me, Takumi!</b></Default>

00:10:51.200 --> 00:10:52.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who's that?</b></Default>

00:10:53.250 --> 00:10:55.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really have no idea.</b></Default>

00:10:56.539 --> 00:10:59.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just what is your acquaintance
here going on about?</b></Default>

00:10:59.330 --> 00:11:01.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This guy is Takumi Fukuyama</b></Default>

00:11:01.620 --> 00:11:03.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and Nene Iwamizawa's boyfriend.</b></Default>

00:11:04.500 --> 00:11:06.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly</b></Default>

00:11:06.159 --> 00:11:08.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of what you guys
are talking about right now.</b></Default>

00:11:08.580 --> 00:11:09.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've said this before</b></Default>

00:11:09.950 --> 00:11:12.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I am Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:11:14.409 --> 00:11:15.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, okay.</b></Default>

00:11:16.200 --> 00:11:18.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you say so, Nene</b></Default>

00:11:19.039 --> 00:11:20.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I believe you.</b></Default>

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:23.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you spare me your time</b></Default>

00:11:24.039 --> 00:11:26.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't really have much time.</b></Default>

00:11:26.500 --> 00:11:27.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be quick.</b></Default>

00:11:28.370 --> 00:11:30.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You probably
don't remember Nene</b></Default>

00:11:30.500 --> 00:11:32.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but this scarf is something
you gave me</b></Default>

00:11:32.500 --> 00:11:34.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on my first birthday</b></Default>

00:11:34.830 --> 00:11:36.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks all tattered.</b></Default>

00:11:36.289 --> 00:11:37.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] Well, yeah.</b></Default>

00:11:37.289 --> 00:11:39.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It has been five winters</b></Default>

00:11:39.330 --> 00:11:41.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You take good care
of your things.</b></Default>

00:11:41.080 --> 00:11:42.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I kind of feel
like it's a good luck charm</b></Default>

00:11:43.039 --> 00:11:44.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I just can't part ways
with it.</b></Default>

00:11:45.289 --> 00:11:47.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wore it
for college entrance exams, too.</b></Default>

00:11:47.830 --> 00:11:49.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Well</b></Default>

00:11:49.450 --> 00:11:51.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I failed when I
was still in high school.</b></Default>

00:11:51.909 --> 00:11:54.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I studied for a year</b></Default>

00:11:55.250 --> 00:11:57.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was when Nene started
saying that it's bad luck</b></Default>

00:11:57.700 --> 00:11:59.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I should throw it away.</b></Default>

00:11:59.450 --> 00:12:01.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-We had a huge argument.
-Oh.</b></Default>

00:12:02.330 --> 00:12:03.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you really
don't have any memories</b></Default>

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:05.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of things like that, do you?</b></Default>

00:12:05.659 --> 00:12:06.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] I mean, you are talking</b></Default>

00:12:06.870 --> 00:12:08.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about your girlfriend</b></Default>

00:12:09.250 --> 00:12:10.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] Do you remember
that I came over here</b></Default>

00:12:10.909 --> 00:12:13.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for entrance exams
and you let me sleep over?</b></Default>

00:12:13.700 --> 00:12:14.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I don't.</b></Default>

00:12:14.950 --> 00:12:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI]
Or how I wore this scarf</b></Default>

00:12:16.330 --> 00:12:18.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for the third entrance exam</b></Default>

00:12:18.450 --> 00:12:20.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What were the results that time?</b></Default>

00:12:20.700 --> 00:12:21.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got accepted.</b></Default>

00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:22.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, congrats.</b></Default>

00:12:23.870 --> 00:12:25.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard from Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:12:25.659 --> 00:12:27.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you bought me a new scarf
the other day.</b></Default>

00:12:28.830 --> 00:12:31.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You came all the way
to the airport to give it to me.</b></Default>

00:12:31.370 --> 00:12:32.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry I couldn't see you.</b></Default>

00:12:34.080 --> 00:12:37.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So really, it's fine
if you don't know about me.</b></Default>

00:12:37.700 --> 00:12:40.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's only natural for me
to be forgotten as well.</b></Default>

00:12:40.450 --> 00:12:41.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I won't forget again.</b></Default>

00:12:42.700 --> 00:12:44.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I won't give up
until you can remember</b></Default>

00:12:44.370 --> 00:12:45.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who I am. Not ever!</b></Default>

00:12:46.330 --> 00:12:47.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However long it takes.</b></Default>

00:12:51.659 --> 00:12:53.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no idea
what you're going on about.</b></Default>

00:12:54.580 --> 00:12:56.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry, but I need to go now.</b></Default>

00:12:56.750 --> 00:12:59.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've forgotten
for close to a year now!</b></Default>

00:12:59.080 --> 00:13:01.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So does that mean you and I
aren't together anymore?</b></Default>

00:13:02.080 --> 00:13:03.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just give me one more chance!</b></Default>

00:13:04.409 --> 00:13:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, go out with me.</b></Default>

00:13:18.450 --> 00:13:19.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Why?</b></Default>

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:21.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why?</b></Default>

00:13:22.409 --> 00:13:24.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because I love you, Nene.</b></Default>

00:13:24.200 --> 00:13:25.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Don't lie to me.</b></Default>

00:13:25.700 --> 00:13:27.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] I'm not lying!</b></Default>

00:13:27.159 --> 00:13:28.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Of course
that can't be true!</b></Default>

00:13:28.620 --> 00:13:29.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's true, I swear!</b></Default>

00:13:29.830 --> 00:13:31.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm nothing
but a pathetic loser!</b></Default>

00:13:31.659 --> 00:13:33.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How could you possibly love me?</b></Default>

00:13:34.330 --> 00:13:36.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came to Tokyo
full of confidence</b></Default>

00:13:36.539 --> 00:13:38.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I didn't get any new jobs
at all!</b></Default>

00:13:39.330 --> 00:13:42.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was merely a model, a name
who belonged to an agency.</b></Default>

00:13:42.580 --> 00:13:44.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really thought
I could make it!</b></Default>

00:13:44.830 --> 00:13:47.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought
I could become someone.</b></Default>

00:13:47.120 --> 00:13:49.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I turned out
to be a total nobody.</b></Default>

00:13:49.620 --> 00:13:51.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And as a poor, lonely loser</b></Default>

00:13:51.909 --> 00:13:54.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all I became
was a fake Touko Kirishima!</b></Default>

00:13:55.450 --> 00:13:56.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nene</b></Default>

00:13:56.909 --> 00:13:58.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is that you?</b></Default>

00:13:58.750 --> 00:14:00.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go ahead, Takumi. Laugh at me.</b></Default>

00:14:01.200 --> 00:14:03.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Laugh at me
because I became just a nobody!</b></Default>

00:14:03.580 --> 00:14:05.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] There's no way
I can laugh at you!</b></Default>

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:06.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] I'm sorry, Takumi.</b></Default>

00:14:07.039 --> 00:14:08.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stop concerning yourself
with me.</b></Default>

00:14:09.409 --> 00:14:11.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nene Iwamizawa
has nothing anymore.</b></Default>

00:14:12.580 --> 00:14:15.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Becoming Touko Kirishima
is my only option.</b></Default>

00:14:15.250 --> 00:14:17.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The person
I fell in love with is Nene!</b></Default>

00:14:17.539 --> 00:14:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nene, just the way she is!</b></Default>

00:14:19.080 --> 00:14:21.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who exactly is me the way I am?</b></Default>

00:14:22.159 --> 00:14:23.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I knew
who such a fine self was</b></Default>

00:14:24.039 --> 00:14:25.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't have any hardships.</b></Default>

00:14:25.789 --> 00:14:27.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if that's the case</b></Default>

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:28.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to believe
that I'm more blessed</b></Default>

00:14:28.659 --> 00:14:31.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than others</b></Default>

00:14:31.409 --> 00:14:34.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to believe above all else
that I am someone!</b></Default>

00:14:35.289 --> 00:14:37.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] You clearly
have a good grasp</b></Default>

00:14:37.120 --> 00:14:38.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-of who you are.
-[grunts softly]</b></Default>

00:14:39.620 --> 00:14:42.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You just showed exactly
who you are, Iwamizawa.</b></Default>

00:14:43.080 --> 00:14:44.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you want to become someone</b></Default>

00:14:44.289 --> 00:14:46.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you can go ahead
and become someone</b></Default>

00:14:46.289 --> 00:14:48.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>an announcer or whatever.</b></Default>

00:14:48.250 --> 00:14:49.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Is that all
that you have to say?</b></Default>

00:14:49.950 --> 00:14:51.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. There's more.</b></Default>

00:14:51.370 --> 00:14:52.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What you just said</b></Default>

00:14:52.870 --> 00:14:55.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about you
having nothing anymore.</b></Default>

00:14:55.120 --> 00:14:57.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's an egotistical thing
to say, don't you think?</b></Default>

00:14:57.659 --> 00:14:59.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you mean?</b></Default>

00:14:59.120 --> 00:15:00.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Look, Iwamizawa</b></Default>

00:15:00.620 --> 00:15:02.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you clearly have Fukuyama.</b></Default>

00:15:02.700 --> 00:15:04.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You still have someone precious</b></Default>

00:15:04.289 --> 00:15:06.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that cherishes you
exactly the way that you are.</b></Default>

00:15:07.700 --> 00:15:10.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wouldn't call somebody
like that a loser, would you?</b></Default>

00:15:10.789 --> 00:15:12.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not when they're loved.</b></Default>

00:15:13.370 --> 00:15:14.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Is that all
you want to say?</b></Default>

00:15:15.539 --> 00:15:16.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:15:19.200 --> 00:15:20.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:15:24.370 --> 00:15:25.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

00:15:29.909 --> 00:15:32.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can say that
with a straight face?</b></Default>

00:15:32.159 --> 00:15:33.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That I'm someone who's loved?</b></Default>

00:15:34.409 --> 00:15:37.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly, Sakuta. Hearing that
from you is annoying.</b></Default>

00:15:37.409 --> 00:15:41.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. For real. Being told that
by Azusagawa is a bit annoying.</b></Default>

00:15:42.000 --> 00:15:43.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess you're right.</b></Default>

00:15:43.909 --> 00:15:45.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I were capable
of thinking that way</b></Default>

00:15:46.450 --> 00:15:49.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>maybe this little life of mine
would be a bit more enjoyable.</b></Default>

00:15:50.500 --> 00:15:52.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So for right now</b></Default>

00:15:52.620 --> 00:15:54.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I can put up
with Takumi.</b></Default>

00:15:54.830 --> 00:15:56.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps, sighs]</b></Default>

00:15:56.870 --> 00:15:58.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] I'm so glad
to hear that.</b></Default>

00:16:02.870 --> 00:16:04.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, stand up.</b></Default>

00:16:04.950 --> 00:16:06.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everything went well?</b></Default>

00:16:06.580 --> 00:16:08.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Can you see her too</b></Default>

00:16:08.120 --> 00:16:10.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I sure can.
I see a laughing Santa Claus</b></Default>

00:16:10.830 --> 00:16:12.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in a miniskirt.</b></Default>

00:16:12.289 --> 00:16:14.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, then all's well
that ends well, I suppose.</b></Default>

00:16:15.409 --> 00:16:16.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on.</b></Default>

00:16:16.700 --> 00:16:18.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think
this is the end yet.</b></Default>

00:16:18.539 --> 00:16:20.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[SAKUTA] Huh?
-I'm not the only...</b></Default>

00:16:21.000 --> 00:16:22.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:16:22.750 --> 00:16:24.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>POLICE CHIEF FOR A DAY
ACTRESS MAI SAKURAJIMA</b></Default>

00:16:24.789 --> 00:16:27.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NATIONAL TRAFFIC SAFETY</b></Default>

00:16:27.580 --> 00:16:29.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:16:32.159 --> 00:16:34.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Takumi and I will look around
for a parking spot.</b></Default>

00:16:34.370 --> 00:16:35.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You get out here.</b></Default>

00:16:35.409 --> 00:16:36.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you so much.</b></Default>

00:16:37.370 --> 00:16:38.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE ANNOUNCER]
<i>Hello, everyone.</i></b></Default>

00:16:38.370 --> 00:16:39.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Thank you all for waiting.</i></b></Default>

00:16:40.039 --> 00:16:42.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I believe we don't need</i>
<i>any introductions here.</i></b></Default>

00:16:42.700 --> 00:16:44.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Today, as our police chief</i>
<i>for a day</b></Default>

00:16:44.750 --> 00:16:46.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>we have the lovely</i>
<i>and renowned actress</b></Default>

00:16:46.909 --> 00:16:48.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Mai Sakurajima.</i></b></Default>

00:16:48.580 --> 00:16:50.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[audience cheering and clapping]</b></Default>

00:16:53.159 --> 00:16:54.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:16:56.620 --> 00:16:58.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What the hell is this?</b></Default>

00:16:58.620 --> 00:16:59.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's the matter?</b></Default>

00:16:59.659 --> 00:17:00.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't see them?</b></Default>

00:17:01.039 --> 00:17:02.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In front of the stage.</b></Default>

00:17:02.080 --> 00:17:03.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are a ton
of Santa Clauses, right?</b></Default>

00:17:04.039 --> 00:17:06.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[IKUMI] Huh? Where?
-[SAKUTA] Right there.</b></Default>

00:17:06.750 --> 00:17:08.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Over there. And there.</b></Default>

00:17:08.660 --> 00:17:10.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's some there, too!</b></Default>

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:11.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are that many of them?</b></Default>

00:17:11.910 --> 00:17:13.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's at least a hundred.</b></Default>

00:17:14.039 --> 00:17:16.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello, everyone</b></Default>

00:17:16.079 --> 00:17:17.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as your police chief for a day.</b></Default>

00:17:17.789 --> 00:17:19.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was appointed today
to help increase</b></Default>

00:17:19.660 --> 00:17:21.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everyone's awareness
of traffic safety.</b></Default>

00:17:22.039 --> 00:17:23.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm Mai Sakurajima.</b></Default>

00:17:23.660 --> 00:17:24.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go!</b></Default>

00:17:25.410 --> 00:17:26.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In fact</b></Default>

00:17:26.450 --> 00:17:28.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I actually obtained
a driver's license of my own</b></Default>

00:17:28.869 --> 00:17:30.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>last year. And by doing so</b></Default>

00:17:30.619 --> 00:17:32.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I strongly feel the need
for traffic safety</b></Default>

00:17:32.789 --> 00:17:35.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and how important
it is to prevent accidents.</b></Default>

00:17:35.539 --> 00:17:37.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Come on, get closer.
-There's room up front!</b></Default>

00:17:39.079 --> 00:17:40.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
This is because no one else</b></Default>

00:17:40.329 --> 00:17:42.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-can see the Santa Clauses.
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:17:42.450 --> 00:17:43.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] It's important
to make an effort</b></Default>

00:17:43.950 --> 00:17:46.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to create a society
with no accidents.</b></Default>

00:17:46.289 --> 00:17:48.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if you
are unfortunately involved</b></Default>

00:17:48.160 --> 00:17:50.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in an accident, there are ways
to become an organ donor</b></Default>

00:17:50.829 --> 00:17:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for someone who requires help
right away.</b></Default>

00:17:52.619 --> 00:17:53.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, get closer already!</b></Default>

00:17:54.039 --> 00:17:56.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN] Watch it! Stop pushing!</b></Default>

00:17:56.250 --> 00:17:57.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all exclaim]</b></Default>

00:17:59.700 --> 00:18:01.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, Mai!</b></Default>

00:18:04.039 --> 00:18:05.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

00:18:08.500 --> 00:18:09.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[mic feedback]</b></Default>

00:18:09.539 --> 00:18:10.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

00:18:11.910 --> 00:18:13.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts softly]</b></Default>

00:18:16.410 --> 00:18:17.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ sad music playing]</b></Default>

00:18:18.039 --> 00:18:19.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:18:21.910 --> 00:18:23.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's all right, everyone.</b></Default>

00:18:23.869 --> 00:18:26.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, just try to remain calm.</b></Default>

00:18:26.829 --> 00:18:28.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's all okay now.</b></Default>

00:18:29.950 --> 00:18:31.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everything is fine!</b></Default>

00:18:38.160 --> 00:18:39.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:18:40.450 --> 00:18:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, Sakuta! Stop moving!</b></Default>

00:18:45.119 --> 00:18:46.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're okay.</b></Default>

00:18:48.200 --> 00:18:49.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft grunts]</b></Default>

00:18:57.539 --> 00:18:59.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thud]</b></Default>

00:19:06.119 --> 00:19:08.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, call an ambulance!</b></Default>

00:19:08.500 --> 00:19:10.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where did all these Santas
come from?</b></Default>

00:19:10.619 --> 00:19:12.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it a Santa event today?</b></Default>

00:19:13.329 --> 00:19:14.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's going on?</b></Default>

00:19:15.000 --> 00:19:16.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct murmurs]</b></Default>

00:19:19.910 --> 00:19:21.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[monitor beeping]</b></Default>

00:19:22.910 --> 00:19:24.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

00:19:27.200 --> 00:19:29.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing here, Futaba?</b></Default>

00:19:29.410 --> 00:19:31.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told you yesterday
that I was worried</b></Default>

00:19:31.410 --> 00:19:33.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'd be heading there as well.</b></Default>

00:19:33.700 --> 00:19:34.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] What about Mai?</b></Default>

00:19:35.410 --> 00:19:36.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] It's fine.
She's all right.</b></Default>

00:19:37.329 --> 00:19:39.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The police are asking her
about what happened.</b></Default>

00:19:41.450 --> 00:19:43.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a strange assortment
of individuals.</b></Default>

00:19:44.000 --> 00:19:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] Well, there's one more.</b></Default>

00:19:46.079 --> 00:19:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[YUUMA] Sakuta, don't go
freaking me out too much, okay?</b></Default>

00:19:49.289 --> 00:19:51.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm pretty sure
it's just a concussion</b></Default>

00:19:51.619 --> 00:19:54.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but have them check you out
thoroughly at the hospital.</b></Default>

00:19:54.869 --> 00:19:57.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly, I didn't think
I'd be in Kunimi's care</b></Default>

00:19:57.450 --> 00:19:59.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so early in his career.</b></Default>

00:20:06.829 --> 00:20:08.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

00:20:09.329 --> 00:20:10.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] Hey. You okay, man?</b></Default>

00:20:10.829 --> 00:20:12.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yep. My head's all good.</b></Default>

00:20:12.579 --> 00:20:14.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They said I could go home
after resting up for a bit.</b></Default>

00:20:15.369 --> 00:20:16.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs in relief]</b></Default>

00:20:16.619 --> 00:20:18.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That means
that we'd just be in your way</b></Default>

00:20:18.079 --> 00:20:19.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if we stay here.
So, we'll head home.</b></Default>

00:20:19.750 --> 00:20:21.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? But wait.
We just got here.</b></Default>

00:20:21.750 --> 00:20:23.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've got to get
to the cram school</b></Default>

00:20:23.200 --> 00:20:24.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'll head out, too.</b></Default>

00:20:24.500 --> 00:20:26.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa, are you okay alone?</b></Default>

00:20:26.950 --> 00:20:29.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I think I'll be fine.
My little sister's here.</b></Default>

00:20:29.789 --> 00:20:31.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Jeez, big brother!
What were you thinking?</b></Default>

00:20:32.000 --> 00:20:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to make you worry
about me.</b></Default>

00:20:33.829 --> 00:20:36.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like there are no issues
for now, so rest assured.</b></Default>

00:20:36.500 --> 00:20:37.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The fact
that you were transported</b></Default>

00:20:37.869 --> 00:20:39.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to a hospital
is already an issue.</b></Default>

00:20:39.950 --> 00:20:41.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] There's Mr. Sakuta!</b></Default>

00:20:42.079 --> 00:20:43.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you guys doing here?</b></Default>

00:20:43.950 --> 00:20:45.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede told me what happened.</b></Default>

00:20:45.950 --> 00:20:47.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mentioned it to Himeji</b></Default>

00:20:47.119 --> 00:20:48.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she said we should head
to the hospital</b></Default>

00:20:48.750 --> 00:20:50.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-during our break.
-Are you gonna be all right</b></Default>

00:20:50.579 --> 00:20:51.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mr. Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:20:51.579 --> 00:20:52.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I'll be fine.</b></Default>

00:20:52.910 --> 00:20:55.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The real question is</b></Default>

00:20:55.450 --> 00:20:56.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You only get an hour break.</b></Default>

00:20:56.950 --> 00:20:58.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, crap! He's right.</b></Default>

00:20:58.829 --> 00:21:01.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-We gotta hurry back.
-Huh? Really? Already?</b></Default>

00:21:02.789 --> 00:21:05.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Well, I guess
we should head back, too.</b></Default>

00:21:05.160 --> 00:21:07.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait here just a little longer</b></Default>

00:21:07.410 --> 00:21:09.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai said she's driving over
and we'll be here soon.</b></Default>

00:21:12.950 --> 00:21:14.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

00:21:14.250 --> 00:21:15.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Mai pants]</b></Default>

00:21:16.079 --> 00:21:17.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Huh?</b></Default>

00:21:17.579 --> 00:21:18.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does the wound hurt?</b></Default>

00:21:19.000 --> 00:21:20.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a lot better now.</b></Default>

00:21:20.660 --> 00:21:22.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really had me freaking out</b></Default>

00:21:23.250 --> 00:21:25.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks to you being there
to catch me, Mai</b></Default>

00:21:25.450 --> 00:21:26.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I managed to get away</b></Default>

00:21:26.539 --> 00:21:28.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with not hitting my head
on the ground.</b></Default>

00:21:28.910 --> 00:21:30.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told you I'd protect you</b></Default>

00:21:32.579 --> 00:21:35.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So, what happened
to all the Santa Claus people?</b></Default>

00:21:35.410 --> 00:21:37.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Seeing you, they came
to their senses.</b></Default>

00:21:37.660 --> 00:21:39.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The police are asking
about their circumstances</b></Default>

00:21:39.789 --> 00:21:40.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>one by one.</b></Default>

00:21:40.829 --> 00:21:43.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard everyone
is saying the same thing.</b></Default>

00:21:43.410 --> 00:21:44.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] The same thing?</b></Default>

00:21:44.910 --> 00:21:47.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] That they all thought
they were Touka Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:21:47.410 --> 00:21:48.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[SAKUTA] Huh.
-[MAI] That's why</b></Default>

00:21:48.500 --> 00:21:50.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they were there.
Because they were concerned</b></Default>

00:21:50.410 --> 00:21:52.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about the rumor
that I was Touka Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:21:52.869 --> 00:21:54.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Luckily for me though</b></Default>

00:21:54.289 --> 00:21:56.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's not like they wanted
to cause me any harm.</b></Default>

00:21:56.700 --> 00:21:59.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, so they didn't arrange
this beforehand?</b></Default>

00:21:59.160 --> 00:22:01.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's right. The police
seemed creeped out</b></Default>

00:22:01.119 --> 00:22:02.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by the whole thing.</b></Default>

00:22:02.200 --> 00:22:03.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I see.</b></Default>

00:22:03.950 --> 00:22:06.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In any case, I'm glad that you
were all right, Mai.</b></Default>

00:22:06.450 --> 00:22:08.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what I
should be saying to you.</b></Default>

00:22:08.619 --> 00:22:10.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh! That's right.</b></Default>

00:22:10.750 --> 00:22:12.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nodoka said
that there was something</b></Default>

00:22:12.160 --> 00:22:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she wanted to tell you.</b></Default>

00:22:13.579 --> 00:22:16.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NODOKA] <i>Don't make big sis</i>
<i>worry, you dumb jerk!</i></b></Default>

00:22:16.160 --> 00:22:18.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I assume you weren't worried
at all then, Toyohama.</b></Default>

00:22:18.950 --> 00:22:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UZUKI]<i> I was very worried</b></Default>

00:22:21.079 --> 00:22:22.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was so incredibly worried</b></Default>

00:22:22.500 --> 00:22:24.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I was only able
to eat three rice balls</b></Default>

00:22:24.500 --> 00:22:25.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before our concert!</b></Default>

00:22:25.869 --> 00:22:27.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] <i>Eating three</i>
<i>should be more</i></b></Default>

00:22:27.250 --> 00:22:28.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>than enough, Zukki.</i></b></Default>

00:22:28.450 --> 00:22:31.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, thanks for protecting
my big sis from me.</b></Default>

00:22:32.869 --> 00:22:35.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I wonder what's going on today.
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:22:35.450 --> 00:22:38.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I connected with a whole lot
of people I know.</b></Default>

00:22:38.660 --> 00:22:40.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The injury was terrible</b></Default>

00:22:40.289 --> 00:22:41.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but perhaps
getting to see everyone</b></Default>

00:22:41.910 --> 00:22:42.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was a good thing.</b></Default>

00:22:43.039 --> 00:22:44.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, you're right.</b></Default>

00:22:44.500 --> 00:22:46.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess it
was a pretty good day.</b></Default>

00:22:46.750 --> 00:22:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ closing theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:22:53.789 --> 00:22:56.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MARCH 31ST</b></Default>

00:22:57.450 --> 00:22:59.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ANNOUNCING THOSE
THAT PASSED THE EXAM!</b></Default>

00:23:01.000 --> 00:23:02.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's there.</b></Default>

00:23:02.500 --> 00:23:03.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:23:03.789 --> 00:23:05.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIORI] Nice, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:23:05.329 --> 00:23:06.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like you passed.</b></Default>

00:23:09.500 --> 00:23:11.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] You took the test too</b></Default>

00:23:11.700 --> 00:23:13.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIORI] Tomorrow
is the music fest</b></Default>

00:23:13.079 --> 00:23:14.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that Mai's performing in.</b></Default>

00:23:14.369 --> 00:23:15.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>People are anticipating</b></Default>

00:23:15.789 --> 00:23:17.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she'll come out
and admit it.</b></Default>

00:23:17.450 --> 00:23:20.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] She denied the rumors
on Coming of Age Day, though.</b></Default>

00:23:20.250 --> 00:23:22.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIORI] The rumors
have flared up again after all.</b></Default>

00:23:22.789 --> 00:23:24.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Well, most
of the self-proclaimed</b></Default>

00:23:24.700 --> 00:23:26.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Touko Kirishimas
have been eliminated</b></Default>

00:23:27.000 --> 00:23:29.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but Mai said she's going
to deny the rumors again</b></Default>

00:23:29.579 --> 00:23:30.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the fest tomorrow.</b></Default>

00:23:31.039 --> 00:23:32.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is she now?</b></Default>

00:23:32.450 --> 00:23:36.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In any case, who exactly
is Touko Kirishima anyway?</b></Default>

00:23:36.539 --> 00:23:39.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What kind of person
do you think she is, huh?</b></Default>

